    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 11th level, your Brand of Castigation exposes a fragment of your foe's essence, leaving them vulnerable to your Crimson Rite feature. Whenever you hit a creature with a weapon for which you have an active crimson rite, you roll an additional hemocraft die when determining the extra damage from the rite.</p><p>Additionally, if a branded creature has the ability to possess a creature or object, has Incorporeal Movement trait or a similar feature, it cannot move through creatures or objects or possess them while branded.</p>",
